      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are honored to present this superlative vehicle, currently maintained in pristine condition. This specimen represents an uncompromising standard of automotive excellence, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original showroom luster. Mechanically impeccable and supported by a rigorous maintenance pedigree, this vehicle is suited for the most fastidious collector or enthusiast. It is, without reservation, one of the finest examples available on the market today.",
