    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is an absolute dream\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one and it seriously looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s spotless inside and out, runs perfectly, and has always been kept tucked away in the garage. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanicals are superlative: the VANOS system has been fully bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has received proactive reinforcement to ensure long-term structural rigidity. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, utilizing the original M-tuned MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry with no bushing deflection. Power is managed by the variable M differential lock for surgical corner exits. The exterior maintains a factory-deep luster with zero paint correction required, housing a pristine Nappa leather cabin. A turn-key specimen for the most discerning automotive purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "2020 model. Showroom condition. Original paint. No mechanical issues. Interior flawless. Clean title. Inspections welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
